Class Board

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mccc.cos210.fp2014.cm.game.Board
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Board
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Represents the piece-centric board of the chess engine. It contains meta information about itself, the position of pieces, and turn info. It also keeps track of information about draw scenarios.
